                                    <span class="fw-bold">SA</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="ms-3">
                                    <h5 class="mb-0">Sarah A.</h5>
                                    <small class="text-muted">Verified Buyer</small>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Testimonial 2 -->
                    <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                        <div class="testimonial-card p-4 h-100">
                            <div class="mb-3">
                                <i class="ri-double-quotes-l fs-1 text-primary"></i>
                            </div>
                            <p class="mb-4">
                                I ordered several soaps as gifts, and they were beautifully packaged. The scents are natural
